38 pages, the main part of this paper will appear in J. Inst. Math.
  Jussieu., and Appendix A (A simple proof of ACC for minimal log discrepancies
  for surfaces) will appear in Acta Math. Sin. (Engl. Ser.)

Will be published in the proceedings of ICCS 2020;
  @Booklet{EasyChair:3183, author = {Paul Hofmann and Zaid Tashman}, title =
  {Hidden Markov Models and their Application for Predicting Failure Events},
  howpublished = {EasyChair Preprint no. 3183}, year = {EasyChair, 2020}}
